  <li>
    <p>
      <strong><em>1</em></strong> <em>Discover.</em> We’ll tell you what we think you’ll need (and won’t need!) for your registry, based on your preferences.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><strong><em>2</em></strong> <em>Create.</em> Build your registry with help from other parents and products from anywhere on the Web.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li class="last">
    <p><strong><em>3</em></strong> <em>Share.</em> Easily share your registry with family and friends.
    </p>
  </li>
</ul>
